{
  "stem": "868.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My brother, I, and my father, we were assigned temporarily into an abandoned movie house, abandoned because constructively, it wasn't up to-- it wasn't safe any, anymore.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we found ourselves there with, I would say, at least 100 men, temporarily sleeping there until they found us permanent hiding places.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had the entire floor to ourselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The benches, the rows of seats had been removed to the balcony.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "At the other end was a screen, and we had mattresses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We didn't stay there long, I would say maybe a week or 10 days, still waiting for permanent hiding places, during which time we went to visit my mother in the convent occasionally.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We didn't stay in that abandoned cinema more than I would say a week or 10 days until the morning of November 6, 1943.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It must have been about 5 o'clock in the morning, loud pounding on the door, continues, insisting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "One of us got up out of his sleep in his pajama, walked to the main door.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But before he could reach it, it burst open.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And a flood of German and SS came, came in immediately surrounding all of us, and with barked orders to immediately gather our stuff, and go outside and load up into the trucks that were waiting.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Some people were beaten, who tried to hide under the mattress.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Others, because they were too slow in gathering their pathetic few things-- I helped my father, who wasn't very agile yet because his wound hadn't healed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we were loaded into the trucks and brought to a place I didn't know, obviously.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But it looked like a huge garrison.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because from-- through the top that covered our truck, I could see huge doors opening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And the truck moved in.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
